<h1 id="minimum-functionality-standards">Minimum functionality standards</h1>
<p>To gain Production access to the Making Tax Digital for Income Tax APIs, your software needs to meet the minimum functionality standards.</p>
<p>Details of minimum functionality standards are now available in the <a href="https://developer.service.hmrc.gov.uk/guides/income-tax-mtd-end-to-end-service-guide/documentation/how-to-integrate.html#minimum-functionality-standards">service guide</a>.</p>
